<figureCitation id="98F21AC48F62FEEC492C53B9FED9FB5A" box="[284,380,1173,1194]" captionStart="PLATE 86" captionStartId="302.[151,233,1880,1903]" captionTargetBox="[203,1376,241,1830]" captionTargetId="figure-79@302.[166,1421,195,1858]" captionTargetPageId="302" captionText="PLATE 86. A, D. Pronotum in lateral view, holotypes. B, C, E. Chelae, holotypes. A. Dryinus barbarus. B. D. asiaticus. C. D. barbarus. D. D. orientalis. E. D. gibbosoides. Scale bar 1.24 mm for A, 0.16 mm for B, 0.36 mm for C, 1.53 mm for D and 0.22 mm for E. (From Olmi 1984)." figureDoi="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.5278682" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/5278682/files/figure.png" pageId="300" pageNumber="301">Plate 86B</figureCitation>
